### Video Player Synchronization
**The "Ghost Playhead" Pattern**:
- Video.js instance emits `timeupdate` at 10Hz (throttled)
- Zustand store debounces to 5Hz for UI updates
- WebSocket transmits at 20Hz only when playing (unicast to room)
- **Interpolation**: If network lags, client interpolates playhead position using last known velocity

